summary.para: This class is available in Office 2007 and above.
When the object is serialized out as xml, it's qualified name is c:dTable.

remarks.format:
## Remarks [!INCLUDE[openxmlnoticeiso](~/includes/openxmlnoticeiso.md)]
**dTable (Data Table)**
This element specifies a data table.
|Parent Elements| |---------------------| |plotArea (§21.2.2.145)|
|Child Elements|Subclause| |--------------------|---------------| |extLst (Chart Extensibility)|§21.2.2.64| |showHorzBorder (Show Horizontal Border)|§21.2.2.181| |showKeys (Show Legend Keys)|§21.2.2.182| |showOutline (Show Outline Border)|§21.2.2.186| |showVertBorder (Show Vertical Border)|§21.2.2.190| |spPr (Shape Properties)|§21.2.2.197| |txPr (Text Properties)|§21.2.2.216|
[*Note*: The W3C XML Schema definition of this element’s content model (CT_DTable) is located in §A.5.1. *end note*]
[!INCLUDE[openxmlnoticeiso](~/includes/openxmlcopyrightiso.md)]
